data.description: You must see to believe all that this charming, updated, 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, attached 2 car garage, pool home on a sprawling +/- 1 acre lot, zoned for horses has to offer. As you enter the home you are welcomed by a cozy screened in front porch. Enjoy a view of the tranquil lake while sipping your morning coffee. From there, walk through the front door into the spacious great room featuring new luxury vinyl tile which continues throughout the home. The wood burning fireplace with a cedar wood mantel and masonry rock wall is a favorite spot for friends and family to gather. Vaulted ceilings adorned with decorative natural wood plank trusses and cedar plank whitewashed walls, are among the additional stunning details in this great room. To the left of the great room sits a beautifully renovated kitchen featuring quartz counters, stainless steel appliances, ceramic tile backsplash and large walk in pantry.  To the right of the great room, the hallway leads you to the primary en-suite bedroom and the two secondary bedrooms and shared bathroom. The large primary bedroom has a spacious walk-in closet and sliding glass doors that open up to the pool and lanai area. The primary bedroom en-suite bathroom has a large glass enclosed ceramic tile walk in shower, an oversized vanity with sink with ample storage space. The secondary bedrooms each have a large window with scenic views of the oversized front yard. They share a large bathroom with a shower-tub combo. A separate laundry room is located just off the great room. As you exit the great room through the sliding doors you enter the large screened in pool and lanai area with a retention wall. The pool area has its own bathroom to keep wet swimmers from having to enter the home. Beyond the pool area, you will find the fenced backyard which has a stable and storage shed. The most unique feature of this property, however, is the insulated, air conditioned 2250 Sqft. workshop with a wood framed mezzanine, plumbing hook up, with garage door and concrete flooring. The owners have converted it into a recreation area with a basketball court as well as party space. This property also includes a whole house plus workshop generator, Kinetico water filtration system to go with the well water. No city utilities. (Septic tank/well water) No HOA! This home has so much potential as as an investment property or your very own compound to live and play! The property is close to I 4 and conveniently located near near OIA, golfing and Central Florida attractions. Call to schedule your private showing.
